728033f-a.title: Queens: Springfield Boulevard - 111th Road
728033f-a.text:
Springfield Boulevard, west side, between 111th Road and 112th
Avenue, viewing south and showing an old Hendrickson house. It was
owned by Mrs. A. Hoyt in 1891 and by D. Wittfinn in 1918.
1922
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection
(2)
The same, at a later date.
March 9, 1927
P. L. Sperr
